channel.title: Havok Online
channel.description:
[center][b][size=14pt]Havok Online[/size][/b][/center]
Havok Online is a RSC server that thrives on pking. Unlike most servers we do not intend you to waste you life training. We allow you to start pking in an enjoyable environment right away! You start with a pre-set bank containing the basic items that will get you started. When you kill someone you earn "pkpoints" which are used to buy better items such as rune. However if you die you will lose 1 pkpoint. Do not worry as you cannot go negative. If your interested in joining us you can find us in my sig.
Here are some provided screenies to show you what to expect.
